Kloeckner Metals UK is required by law to publish an annual gender pay gap report.

• This is its report for the snapshot date of 5 April 2017.
• The mean gender pay gap for Kloeckner Metals UK is -10.56%
• The median gender pay gap for Kloeckner Metals UK is -15.37%.
• The mean gender bonus gap for Kloeckner Metals UK is 15.78%.
• The median gender bonus gap for Kloeckner Metals UK is 0%.
• The proportion of male employees in Kloeckner Metals UK receiving a bonus is 69.65%  
and the proportion of female employees receiving a bonus is 73.8%.

