How does Kloeckner Metals UK’s gender pay gap compare with that of other organisations?

The vast majority of organisations have a gender pay gap, and we are pleased to be able to say that 
Kloeckner Metals UK’s gap compares favourably with that of other organisations. 

The mean gender pay gap for the whole economy (according to the November 2016 Office for National 
Statistics (ONS) Annual Survey of Hours and Earnings (ASHE) figures) is 17.5%, At minus 10.56% 

